    "subType": "mutation",
    "description": "<p>As a Main Action, accept one System Strain and target a visible creature. The target gets a Mental saving throw; if they succeed, you simply get a one-sentence description of what they&rsquo;re thinking about right now. If they fail, you get that description and can ask their memories one question, getting a one or two-sentence answer if the question is one their memories could answer. A creature can be targeted by this mutation only once per day, and will not normally notice it even if they succeed in their save.</p>",
